---
title: Southwestern-Style Pork Tacos with Tomato-Lime Salsa and Cheddar Cheese
description: So easy, fast and packed with flavour. Simple should be the middle name of this dish. Sweet peppers and onions pair perfectly with tender pork for a fun taco meal that all comes together with our fabulous Southwest spice blend!
